OL,3,CUK to ban 'sim farms' used by scammers
OL,4,Cto send mass fraud messages
OL,6,FSim farm devices capable of holding
OL,7,Fmultiple sim cards enabling scammers
OL,8,Fto send thousands of scam text
OL,9,Fmessages at once are to be banned
OL,10,Funder plans to crack down on fraud.
OL,12,FThe ban, the first of its kind in
OL,13,FEurope, will make the possession or
OL,14,Fsupply of the devices without good
OL,15,Freason illegal, with unlimited fines
OL,16,Fin England and Wales and a #5,000 fine
OL,17,Fin Scotland and Northern Ireland.
