OL,3,CUK to ban 'sim farms' used by scammers
OL,4,Cto send mass fraud messages
OL,6,FFraud minister Lord Hanson said:
OL,7,F"Fraud devastates lives, and I am
OL,8,Fdetermined to take the decisive action
OL,9,Fnecessary to protect the public from
OL,10,Fthese shameful criminals.
OL,12,F"Two-thirds of British adults say
OL,13,Fthey've received a suspicious message
OL,14,Fon their phone ` equivalent to more
OL,15,Fthan 35 million people ` which is why
OL,16,Fcracking down on sim farms is so vital
OL,17,Fto protecting the public.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOU
