OL,3,CUK to ban 'sim farms' used by scammers
OL,4,Cto send mass fraud messages
OL,6,F"This marks a leap forward in our
OL,7,Ffight against fraud and will provide
OL,8,Flaw enforcement and industry partners
OL,9,Fwith the clarity they need to protect
OL,10,Fthe public from this shameful crime.
OL,12,F"This Government will continue to take
OL,13,Frobust action to protect the public
OL,14,Ffrom fraud and deliver security and
OL,15,Fresilience through the Plan for
OL,16,FChange."
