OL,3,CUK to ban 'sim farms' used by scammers
OL,4,Cto send mass fraud messages
OL,6,FNick Sharp, deputy director for fraud
OL,7,Fat the National Crime Agency (NCA),
OL,8,Fsaid: "Fraud is the crime we are all
OL,9,Fmost likely to experience, and one
OL,10,Fthat causes victims significant
OL,11,Femotional and financial harm.
OL,13,F"We know that fraud at scale is being
OL,14,Ffacilitated by sim farms, which give
OL,15,Fcriminals a means and an opportunity
OL,16,Fto contact victims at scale with
OL,17,Frelative ease.
OL,26,@pD@GOUuD@AOU
