OL,3,CUK to ban 'sim farms' used by scammers
OL,4,Cto send mass fraud messages
OL,6,F"The ban announced today is very
OL,7,Fwelcome. It will give us a vital tool
OL,8,Fto step up our fight against
OL,9,Ffraudsters, target the services they
OL,10,Frely on, and better protect the
OL,11,Fpublic."
OL,13,FThe Government said the new ban will
OL,14,Fcome into effect six months after the
OL,15,FCrime and Policing Bill receives royal
OL,16,Fassent.
