OL,3,CUK to ban 'sim farms' used by scammers
OL,4,Cto send mass fraud messages
OL,6,FScam text messages have become an
OL,7,Fincreasingly common problem in recent
OL,8,Fyears, with mobile operators regularly
OL,9,Fintroducing new technology to help
OL,10,Fspot and block them before they reach
OL,11,Fthe public.
OL,13,FRachel Andrews, head of corporate
OL,14,Fsecurity at Vodafone UK, said the ban
OL,15,Fon sim farms was an "important step"
OL,16,Fin preventing fraud.
OL,18,F"Vodafone UK is committed to
OL,19,Fprotecting all our customers from
OL,20,Ffraud, including activity enabled by
OL,21,Fsim farms," she said.
