OL,3,CUK to ban 'sim farms' used by scammers
OL,4,Cto send mass fraud messages
OL,6,F"So far this year we have blocked over
OL,7,F38.5 million suspected scam messages,
OL,8,Fand in 2024 that figure reached over
OL,9,F73.5 million for the year.
OL,11,F"As an industry, UK telecoms operators
OL,12,Fhave blocked more than one billion
OL,13,Fsuspected scam messages since 2023.
OL,15,F"However, we cannot fully tackle fraud
OL,16,Fin isolation; collaboration between
OL,17,Findustry and government is crucial.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUwD@AOU
