OL,3,CUK to ban 'sim farms' used by scammers
OL,4,Cto send mass fraud messages
OL,6,F"This is a really important step taken
OL,7,Fby the Home Office and we fully
OL,8,Fsupport the inclusion of sim farms in
OL,9,Fthe upcoming legislation.
OL,11,F"We look forward to working together
OL,12,Fon this issue."
OL,14,FShadow home secretary Chris Philp
OL,15,Fsaid: "We welcome this move but let's
OL,16,Fnot pretend Labour led the charge.
OL,17,FThis builds directly on the work the
OL,18,FConservatives did last year to crack
OL,19,Fdown on sim farms through the Criminal
OL,20,FJustice Bill.
