OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F304A1745452888
OL,3,CUK to ban 'sim farms' used by scammers
OL,4,Cto send mass fraud messages
OL,6,F"These devices are the weapon of
OL,7,Fchoice for fraudsters. We acted to
OL,8,Fclose that loophole, and it's right
OL,9,Fthat Labour are finally scrambling to
OL,10,Fcatch up.
OL,12,F"Enforcement is now key, as criminals
OL,13,Fwill always look for new ways to abuse
OL,14,Fthe system. Ministers must ensure this
OL,15,Flegislation is watertight, or it risks
OL,16,Fbeing a ban in name only."
